0094     /**
0095      * Creates a hierarchical boolean property.
0096      * Returns the {@code property}'s value if present, otherwise check's if the supplied
0097      * {@code provider} is not null and returns its value, otherwise returns the {@code defaultValue}.
0098      *
0099      * @param providers the {@code Provider} factory used to create a {@code Provider}.
0100      * @param property the property to use
0101      * @param provider the provider to use
0102      * @param defaultValue the default value in case neither property nor provider has one
0103      * @return property's value, provider's value, or the defaultValue, in that order.
0104      */
0105     static <E extends Enum<E>> Provider<E> enumProvider(ProviderFactory providers,
0106                                                         Property<E> property,
0107                                                         Provider<E> provider,
0108                                                         E defaultValue) {
0109         providers.provider {
0110             switch (resolvePropertyPriority()) {
0111                 case Priority.PROPERTY:
0112                     return property.getOrElse(provider ? provider.getOrElse(defaultValue) : defaultValue)
0113                 case Priority.PROVIDER:
0114                     return provider ? provider.getOrElse(property.getOrElse(defaultValue)) : property.getOrElse(defaultValue)
0115             }
0116         }
0117     }
0118 
0119     static <E extends Enum<E>> Provider<E> enumProvider(ProviderFactory providers,
0120                                                         Property<E> property,
0121                                                         Provider<E> provider,
0122                                                         Provider<E> defaultValue) {
0123         providers.provider {
0124             switch (resolvePropertyPriority()) {
0125                 case Priority.PROPERTY:
0126                     return property.orElse(provider ? provider.orElse(defaultValue) : defaultValue).get()
0127                 case Priority.PROVIDER:
0128                     return (provider ? provider.orElse(property.orElse(defaultValue)) : property.orElse(defaultValue)).get()
0129             }
0130         }
0131     }

0133     /**
0134      * Creates a {@code Provider} that resolves values from additional sources if the property's value is not set.
0135      *
0136      * @param envKey the environment variable to check.
0137      * @param propertyKey the system and project property to check.
0138      * @param property the property to check value from.
0139      * @param order resolving order to use.
0140      * @param path resolving path to use.
0141      * @param project a project.
0142      * @param owner the Object that owns the property.
0143      * @return the property's value if set or a value resolved based on the {@code order} argument.
0144      */
0145     @CompileDynamic
0146     static <E extends Enum<E>> Provider<E> enumProvider(String envKey,
0147                                                         String propertyKey,
0148                                                         Class<E> enumType,
0149                                                         Property<E> property,
0150                                                         Order order,
0151                                                         Path path,
0152                                                         Project project,
0153                                                         Object owner,
0154                                                         E defaultValue) {
0155         project.providers.provider {
0156             switch (resolvePropertyPriority()) {
0157                 case Priority.PROPERTY:
0158                     if (property.present) return property.get()
0159                     String value = resolveValue(envKey, propertyKey, order, path, project, owner)
0160                     if (isNotBlank(value)) {
0161                         return enumType.valueOf(value.toUpperCase())
0162                     }
0163                     return defaultValue
0164                 case Priority.PROVIDER:
0165                     String value = resolveValue(envKey, propertyKey, order, path, project, owner)
0166                     if (isNotBlank(value)) {
0167                         return enumType.valueOf(value.toUpperCase())
0168                     }
0169                     return property.getOrElse(defaultValue)
0170             }
0171         }
0172     }

3713                 }

3716                     if (isBlank(value)) value = System.getenv(envKey)
3717                     if (isBlank(value)) value = System.getProperty(propertyKey)
3718                 }
3719                 if (isBlank(value) && projectAccess) {
3720                     value = (project.findProperty(propertyKey) as String)
3721                 }
3722                 return value
3723             }
3724             case Order.PROP_SYS_ENV: PSE:

3750     @CompileDynamic
3751     private static String resolvePath(Object object) {
3752         if (object instanceof PathAware) {
3753             return ((PathAware) object).path
3754         } else if (object instanceof Task) {
3755             return ((Task) object).path
3756         } else if (object?.metaClass?.respondsTo('getPath')) {
3757             return object.getPath()
3758         }
3759         return object ? object.class.name.replaceAll('.', ':') : ''
3760     }

3762     private static String normalizePath(String path, String delimiter) {
3763         if (':' == path || '' == path) {
3764             return ''
3765         }
3766         return path[1..-1].replace(':', delimiter).replace(' ', '_') + delimiter
3767     }
